ass=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B46530008</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">White</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$81.73 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/2/E21E0D41AECB16B9C1E46ACA93BFD4BE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B46530009</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">White</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$81.73 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/2/E21E0D41AECB16B9C1E46ACA93BFD4BE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B465300010</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">White</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$81.73 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Men's Snap-Front Cotton Coverall - CC14. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">CC14</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>10 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">1</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}